{{for|other uses|Blaze}} {{Infobox XC3 Status |title = Blaze |caption = Deals damage at fixed intervals. |image = XC3 Blaze Icon.png |type = Debuff |attribute = Ether |base-duration = 10.0s |max-duration = 20.0s |success-rate = 100% |rng-applicable = No |effect-title-1 = Base Damage (per tick) |effect-value-1 = 8% of Art damage |effect-title-2 = Tick Duration |effect-value-2 = 1.0s }} '''Blaze''' is a [[Status Effect]] in {{XC3}} and {{XC3FR|sublink}}. It deals damage at fixed intervals.
== Distribution == === Arts === * [[Empyrean Salvo (XC3)|Empyrean Salvo]] ([[Seraph]]) * [[Inferno Dance]] (Seraph) * [[Flame Nova (XC3)|Flame Nova]] ([[Sena]], [[Ouroboros]]) * [[Atomize]] ([[Taion]], Ouroboros) * [[Heavenly Spear]] ([[Cammuravi]]) * [[Illusory Bloom (FR)|Illusory Bloom]] ([[Kitharode]])
=== Field Effects === These field effects deal damage over time, and are marked as having Blaze effects, though they do not actually apply the debuff. The field effects' damage are based on the user's Attack rather than being tied to Art damage, and their tick durations may also differ from that of the debuff. * [[Energy Grenade]] ([[Yumsmith]]; 50% of Attack power per 1.0s) * [[Roasty-Toasty]] ([[Riku & Manana]]; 50% of Attack power per 1.0s) * [[Pride of Place]] ([[Lapidarist]]; 100% of Attack power per 2.0s) * Lambda Pressure ([[Lambda Ferronis]]; 60% of Attack power per 3.0s) * Heat Injection ([[Gastrates]]; 35% of Attack power per 2.0s) * Ultra Heat Injection ([[Dorrick]]) * Extension Injection ([[Stronghammer Dorga]]; 35% of Attack power per 2.0s) * Kevesi Termination Order (Stronghammer Dorga; 35% of Attack power per 2.0s)
