{{for|other uses|Blowdown}}
[[File:XC3 Blowdown.png|thumb]]
'''Blowdown''' is a reaction status in {{XC3}} and {{XC3FR|sublink}}. It tosses targets backwards into the air, interrupting their current attack and momentarily preventing them from attacking while they get back up. It staggers targets for longer than [[Knockback (XC3)|Knockback]] and takes priority over it. It can be inflicted by certain [[Battle Arts (XC3)|Battle Arts]] and by some enemy attacks. In {{XC3FR|sub}}, Blowdown can only be inflicted by certain [[Unity|Unity Combos]] on [[Launch (XC3)|launched]] enemies.

Certain enemies have resistance or immunity to the status.

